and Southern Sections. 05,19,07,06,06,04 School Sect. Div. Rec. LW 1. Mater Dei 
SS I 14-0 2 2. Los Alamitos SS I 12-1 3 3. Bishop Amat SS I 13-1 1 4. Sylmar 
