<TEXT>
<P>
 Although quarterback Chris Chandler failed to inspire the troops, Coach Chuck 
Knox said he will start again Sunday against the Bears in Chicago. 
</P>
<P>
 "I don't see any reason to change," Knox said."Chandler had the misfortune of 
