<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Lana Turner -- A story about Lana Turner in Saturday's Calendar section 
incorrectly implied that the actress had died. Turner, 74, is a resident of 
Century City, and in September accepted a lifetime achievement award at the San 
Sebastian International Cinema Festival in Spain, Europe's oldest film 
festival. 
</P>
