<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Prep wrestling -- A story in Thursday's Times Orange County implied that 
Calvary Chapel contacts wrestlers in an attempt to recruit them. Recruiting is 
against CIF-Southern Section rules. The success of the Eagles' program has 
helped attract many transfer students to the private school. 
</P>
